  "2268560": {
    "name": "在线丧尸生存游戏",
    "steam_appid": 2268560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《在线丧尸生存游戏》</strong>中，你将与同伴并肩作战，凭借智慧、火力和勇气，在活死人横行的末</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世中艰难求生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >险象环生的地形、暗藏的资源、无尽的故事，正待你一一揭晓！但切记，危险如影随形——时刻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持警惕，严阵以待，否则你将沦陷于<strong>《在线丧尸生存游戏》</strong>的恐怖深渊……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/5d39aa8a0d2616b7211141728497219e.poster.avif?t=1770486186\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/5d39aa8a0d2616b7211141728497219e.webm?t=1770486186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们希望为新生代玩家重现我们团队老玩家当年的热血激情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，老一辈玩家同样也能在我们对经典游戏的致敬中找回熟悉的感动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是初出茅庐还是久经沙场，<strong>备好弹药，装好手电，勇敢踏入《在线丧尸生存游戏》这变幻</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>莫测的末日世界吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/417209f19600078e91f9ffafea6b6139.avif?t=1770486186\" width=620 height=253 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《在线丧尸生存游戏》提供多种玩法选择，任你探索。你可以独自挑战，看看没有队友拖后腿，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能走多远；也可以组队合作，向队友证明，你在丧尸肆虐的荒原上是不可或缺的伙伴；还可以</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入多人模式，助人为乐或掠夺他人资源。你的选择，决定一切！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心游戏机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《在线丧尸生存游戏》中，你需要搜集稀缺资源、建造坚实基地、制作各式道具，不断锤炼生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存技艺。无论昼夜，变幻莫测的天气都可能带来致命挑战。做好准备，否则你可能沦落到一无所</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/ad37447ae39c8172862e42d047d50546.poster.avif?t=1770486186\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/ad37447ae39c8172862e42d047d50546.webm?t=1770486186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器多样</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量武器，助你找到最契合你独特玩法的神兵利器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/162488699df65c8c075633f6130385b1.avif?t=1770486186\" width=475 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现已推出9款武器，未来还将不断扩充武器库！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以玩家为核心的开发理念</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们以玩家反馈为驱动，持续优化现有内容、新增功能，打造健康和谐的游戏环境。在玩家的指</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引下，我们力求提供最优质的游戏体验，让你沉浸其中，同时不断调整和移除与游戏愿景不符的</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/012373779338b5e19a32e39942abbe5e.poster.avif?t=1770486186\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/012373779338b5e19a32e39942abbe5e.webm?t=1770486186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的丧尸AI</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完善丧尸行为不是件容易的事，不过它们已经不再是只会傻站着抬头尖叫的活靶子了！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义地图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >期待玩家社区探索这片精心打造的自定义地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图名称将由社区共同决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/526f8e969d7e2f8d44d59f3bf02eb7d3.avif?t=1770486186\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras_big/526f8e969d7e2f8d44d59f3bf02eb7d3.avif?t=1770486186 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图横跨4公里见方，众多独特地点等你探索，各有其独特的挑战与奖励。从繁华都市到隐藏在</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >森林中的小彩蛋，你的冒险之旅将充满惊喜。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >音乐爱好者福音！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《在线丧尸生存游戏》汇聚了众多音乐人才，为游戏量身打造配乐。但在制作原创音乐的过程中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >，不少曲目遗憾落选。为了不让这些心血白费，我们在游戏内设计了电台功能。探索地图，你将</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现不少播放着106.9 末日审判频道的收音机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/d6991a8a76be84c408a1c7dd957902d0.avif?t=1770486186\" width=624 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >枪战机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《在线丧尸生存游戏》的枪战和第一人称射击体验将让你眼前一亮。无论面对丧尸群、守望空旷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原野，还是都市屋顶露营，你总能找到心仪的武器和玩法。我们的动画总是在写实中透着一丝科</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幻，但在这丧尸末世中，可别被这些小巧思分了神……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/193da347867c7399d3e41b7749cb2c1d.poster.avif?t=1770486186\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/193da347867c7399d3e41b7749cb2c1d.webm?t=1770486186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏商人和背景故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内现有12位个性鲜明的商人，其背景故事紧密相连。虽然目前展示故事的方式有限，但未来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >，我们将增加与这些角色的互动，让你能够接取任务，赚取声望点。至于现在，你可以在商人间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交易物资，并在地图各处寻找线索，逐步揭开游戏背景故事的神秘面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2268560/extras/61a346b44cfcb0558c1395fa3a06bdfa.avif?t=1770486186\" width=620 height=253 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发团队向你问好</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gibby</strong>是我们的游戏体验和公司管理专家，带领团队井然有序、专注高效，助我们在快节奏、竞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >争激烈的游戏开发行业中稳步前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ear</strong>在网游界摸爬滚打超过10年，是头脑风暴的高手。他擅长关卡设计，也负责维护网站运行，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作室里的部分热门音乐同样出自他手。这可是位生存游戏硬核爱好者，地图里少不了他藏的彩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蛋，大家可要擦亮眼睛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jest</strong>是我们外聘的程序天才！他知识丰富，技能全面，负责确保游戏流畅运行，同时不断创新机</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SuperPoggers</strong>是《在线丧尸生存游戏》的专属AI助手，为游戏后端基础设施管理提供咨询和指</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >导，确保在线体验顺畅。SuperPoggers也负责在游戏设计决策中给出反馈，分析决策对玩法策略</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >的影响。</p>",
